    <string name="introduction">Welcome to use the \"Barcode Toolbox\" app!\nThis app not only provides scanning and identification functions for various codes, but also provides construction functions.\nSupports importing pictures from external apps for scanning. Just choose to open or share the picture in the external app and select this app.\nWhile scanning the code content, various valid information can be parsed and extracted, without having to dwell on the meaning of the original string.\nThe construction function is still in Beta stage. Any problems can be reported to the developer at any time.\nThe following functions support scanning multiple codes in one image:\nImage file scanning, camera scanning\n\nDeveloper: Coolapk@威尼斯的向日葵</string>

